summary: AN ORDINANCE carrying over the unexpended and unencumbered balances in certain 1973 Budget appropriations made from the General, Parks and Recreation, Library, Seattle Center, Seattle Parking Commission, City Street, Arterial City Street, Light, Water, Sewer, Engineering Department Operating, Building Department Operating, manpower and Youth Operating, Community Development Operating, Art Commission Operating, Emergency Employment Operating and Employees Retirement Funds to the respective items in the 1974 Budget.
